These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue
City: san-francisco, marseilles
House: craftsman, cape-cod
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, spy
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
5. the person watching spy movies is the cape-cod house##1
6. the person who growsazalea is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Color      | blue        | chestnut |
| City          | marseilles  | san-francisco     |
| House         | cape-cod    | craftsman         |
| Flower           | iris    | azalea |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | malaysian     |
| Birthday           | november      | april    |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | adventure          |

