2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating onion##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Flower         | daisy      | azalea       |
| City           | hannover | boston |
| Food   | pear      | onion        |
| Color   | blood-red         | mauve        |
